    "dhp222:2": "vāraye → dhāraye (bj, sya-all, pts1ed, pts2ed) ",
    "dhp224:2": "dajjā appampi → dajjā'ppasmimpi (bj); dajjā appasmi (sya-all, pts2ed, mr); dajjā appasmiṁ (pts1ed) ",
    "dhp225:1": "Ahiṁsakā ye munayo → ahiṁsakāyā munayo (mr) ",
